"Ofcourse." CYCLONUS said as he nodded respectfully to HYDRAS.
Flipping on his radio CYCLONUS orders the troops to be meet them
outside.

SCOURGE answered quickly enough, followed by DEEPSTRKE. Both of them
would be outside. PHOBIA would of couse be with DEEPSTRYKE.

There was no answer from NIGHTRAZOR, except for a short click from his
radio, CYCLONUS and DEEPSTRYKE well knew he would be there.

INFERNO was already moving to HYDRAS' said as the call was going out,
and WASPINATOR as well.

INSECTICON and IGUANUS were also running towards the doior to preapre
for the coming event.

SKYSHADOW was leading his team outside, behind him was INJECTOR,
BUZZCLAW, TERRORGATOR and QUICKSTRIKE, the Predaon fuzors, all ready
for action.

There were at the last three left, TARANTULUS, FRACTYL and BRUTICUS-X
who were to be left behind to watch over the base.

BRUTICUS was standing there with his massive axe in his hand.
"Everything shall be as you leave it." he said to HYDRAS and CYCLONUS.

"And we shall continue to work on repairs." FRACTLY said. "Yeah . . .
what he said." TARANTULUS said noncommittedly.

Meanwhile the base sensors were still picking up on the massive heard
of Dinosaurs that seems to be stampedeing across an area as wide as a
state, and they showed no signs of stopping! They would be on HYDRAS'
new base within an 3 hours if they did not stop!
